comments: Aldridge (SAS) has a marginal hand to Osman's (CLE) side, but doesn't apply any force that affects his ability to defend.
DeRozan (SAS) and Love (CLE) engage and separate off-ball.
Nance Jr. (CLE) sets the screen in Mills' (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
DeRozan (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Love (CLE).
Osman (CLE) makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) body at the start of his drive.
Nance Jr. (CLE) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Nance Jr. (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Belinelli (SAS).
Belinelli (SAS) briefly grasps Love's (CLE) shorts during the pick, but doesn't affect his FOM.
Love (CLE) is in a wide picking position in Belinelli's (SAS) path when lower leg contact occurs, but the contact is marginal.
[Observable in enhanced video] Nance Jr. (CLE) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Aldridge (SAS) makes marginal contact to Nance Jr.'s (CLE) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his play at the basket.
Osman (CLE) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (SAS) that doesn't affect his SQBR during the off-ball screen.
Aldridge (SAS) sets the pick in Love's (CLE) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Nance Jr. (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position during Gay's (SAS) driving shot attempt.
LLB shows Love (CLE) grabs and pulls Aldridge's (SAS) jersey away from his body during the rebound.
LLS shows Gay (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from Osman (CLE) after the rebound.
LAR shows Nance Jr. (CLE) extends his arm into Aldridge (SAS) and dislodges him towards Osman (CLE).   Osman's ability to defend is not affected as he goes away from any contact with Aldridge..
Love (CLE) makes marginal contact with Aldridge (SAS) as he disengages from the contact.
Aldridge (SAS) legally contests Love's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
LAR shows Sexton (CLE) initiates contact to White's (SAS) backside that affects his ability to rebound.
Sexton (CLE) dislodges Gay (SAS) after he gathers the rebound.
